title: Worms.Revolution.Gold.Edition-PROPHET
description:
Worms Revolution Gold Edition-PROPHET

Worms: Revolution is an upcoming artillery strategy game developed by Team17 and is part of the Worms series. It will be released on Playstation 3, Windows via Steam and Xbox 360 in October 2012. Like previous games in the series, gameplay is 2D and turn-based, but it is rendered with an all-new 3D engine. There will be both single player and multiplayer modes with up to four players online or local hotseat. The game will have a completely new engine.


Content Included:

PreOrder DLC
Mars Pack
Funfair DLC
Medieval Tales DLC
Customization Pack DLC

Languages: EN/FR/DE/IT/ES/PL/RU/CZ
